# How to Create and Restore a Boot Volume Backup in Oracle Cloud
#### [Made by Birzu Adrian with Scribe](https://scribehow.com/shared/How_to_Create_and_Restore_a_Boot_Volume_Backup_in_Oracle_Cloud__hxpxFZRVS7SdrmyxBrpxow)


