ssh -i 'C:\Users\opc\Downloads\id_rsa' -N -L 80:10.101.1.73:80 -p 22 ocid1.bastionsession.oc1.eu-frankfurt-1.amaaaaaagysxq7aaskwrj5cw2as2t6edirjnasncla5vrzfqwnrsnwk7zmsa@host.bastion.eu-frankfurt-1.oci.oraclecloud.com**

